query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 0
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('artifactory',
'azure-functions',
'cluster-computing',
'crud',
'dropdown',
'inversion-of-control',
'mean-stack',
'replication',
'sql-server-2016',
'subset',
'uitextview',
'watir',
'xcode6');
